nodes.title: U.S. airstrike kills scores of Shabab militants at Somalia training camp, Pentagon says
nodes.summary:
A major U.S. airstrike in Somalia has killed more than 150 fighters belonging to Shabab, the Al Qaeda-affiliated group that has carried out lethal bombings and attacks across the Horn of Africa, the Pentagon said Monday.

The Saturday night air attack appears to be the deadliest the U.S. has conducted...
